snippet.title: Free Holiday Update Drops on Sky Runner
snippet.description:
Sky Runner has been updated to 1.1 with loads of quality of life changes. 

The drone simulator on Quest is getting better and better with move updates planned for 2025. The team wanted to celebrate 2024 by going out with a bang – 1.1. Brings updated graphics and a limited time mode. Help deliver presents anywhere in the world through the power of mixed reality. Flat2VR Studios is working with Toys for Tots to help bring action into the digital real into the real world. 

For more information check out this document: https://docs.google.com/document/u/2/d/1FTODO-KNeCWEV3JYu-YuPz-BFbWp40K7xQhOZeZ7seU/

https://www.meta.com/experiences/sky-runner/25082836531303488/
